<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039110" n="1"/> 
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-1012090132" type="person">Andream Ritsium</rs>, <rs key="place_GEO-2959508" type="place">Adelshemium</rs>.</note>
 
  <p><rs type="lostletter">Literas</rs> tuas suavissimas, quas <date>9. Julii</date> ad me dedisti, sub finem <date>ejusdem mensis</date> accepi, inclusasque
    <lb/><abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104222069" type="person">Im Hof</rs> tradidi, qui <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quali mecum desiderio expectabat nuntium de tuo <rs key="place_GEO-2959508" type="place">Adelshemium</rs> ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ventu. Quemadmodum autem non leve fuit gaudium, quo me perfudisti, cum te eodem ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>venisse, munusque tuum felicibus auspiciis aggressum fuisse significares; ita non leviter
    <lb/>i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>inuit hoc gaudium dolor gravissimus, quem ex infortunio, quod tibi in itinere accidit,
    <lb/>concepi, adeo ut etiam nunquam desiissem dolere, nisi te feliciter restitutum esse addi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>disses. Deus tibi inposterum valetudinem perpetuam, et omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tibi utilia et
    <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue ad gubernationem Ecclesi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> necessaria esse novit, largiatur! Nihil scio,
    <lb/>quod tibi amplius solvendum sit propter Magisterium capessitum, nisi forsan <rs type="person">Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
      <pb facs="1039111" n="2"/>
      <lb break="no"/>motori</rs> vestro, qui <rs type="biblio">Progra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ata</rs> impressit, circiter 12<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> bazeni; volebat ille, ut ego, quia <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
    <lb/>te substitutus essem, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> singulis Candidatis <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quod alias primus Candidatorum facere debet<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice>
    <lb/>exigerem sumtus in <rs type="biblio">Progra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ata</rs> imprimenda factos, facile autem potes judicare, quomodo
    <lb/>ridiculo huic petito satisfecerim. Ex illo tempore neque ipse neque <rs type="person">Pedellus</rs> quicquam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me
    <lb/>petiit, nihil autem petenti nihil dabitur. <rs key="pers_no_GND_id" type="person">Zörnlinus</rs> mihi misit duorum a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>orum <rs type="biblio">catalog<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>plurium confectionem, quia negotia alia mihi supervenerunt, ipsum differre jussi, quod<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cunque ipsi dedisses stren<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nomine, placuisset, melius enim quam ego laborem ejus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stima<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re potes. Gratum mihi erit, si quomodo se habeat rerum tuarum status, subinde nuntia<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bis, <rs type="letter">literas</rs> quibus me dignaberis poteris <rs key="place_GEO-2934469" type="place">Durlacum</rs> mittere ad <rs type="person">Amicum</rs> quendam, qui vo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>catur <abbr><rs type="person">D. D. S.</rs></abbr> per quem etiam hasce tibi mitto, hoc mediante possumus co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ercium nostrum
    <lb/>literarium instituere, dummodo curemus, ut liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <hi rend="u">franc<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice></hi> ad ipsum perveniant. </p>
<closer><salute>Vale et
  <lb/>amare perge tui studiosissimum </salute><signed>NB. </signed> <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1708-08-08">8. Augusti 1708</date>.</dateline>
</closer>
</div>
</body>
